	</head>
	<body>
		<p style="font-size:20px; color:blue; font-family: Arial">A truly spectacular paragraph!</p>
	</body>
</html>

Codecademy HTML & CSS ANSWERS HTML Basics II /Background color/12

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Sexy background color!</title>
	</head>
	<body style="background-color:brown;">
		<h3>Favorite Football Teams</h3>
			<ol style="background-color:yellow;">
			<ol>
				<li>The Hawthorn Football Club</li>	
				<li>San Franscisco 49ers</li>
				<li>Barcelona FC</li>
			</ol>
		</p>
	</body>
</html>

Codecademy HTML & CSS ANSWERS HTML Basics II /Aligning the text/13

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Sexy background color!</title>
	</head>
	<body>
	<h3 style="text-align:center">
     Favorite Football Teams</h3>
     
			<ol>
				<li style="text-align:left">The Hawthorn Football Club</li>	
				<li style="text-align:center">San Franscisco 49ers</li>
				<li style="text-align:right">Barcelona FC</li>
			</ol>			
	</body>
</html>

Codecademy HTML & CSS ANSWERS HTML Basics II /Strong words!/14

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Viva La Revolution!</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<p>Do you hear the people <strong>sing</strong>?</p>
		<p>No I don't. I'm <strong>too</strong> busy eating cake.</p>
	</body>
</html>

Codecademy HTML & CSS ANSWERS HTML Basics II /Emphasize words!/15

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Some nice practice</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<p>Hey, don't say<em> that</em>!</p>
		<p>I am <em>so</em> tired.</p>
	</body>
</html>

Codecademy HTML & CSS ANSWERS HTML Basics II /Summary/16

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title></title>
	</head>
	<body style="background-color:red; text-align:center";>
	<font size="5px"; face="Arial"; color="green">
	Bangladesh District List </font>
	<ol>My Country>
	 <li> Bangladesh>
	 <ul> District list </ul> </li>
	 </ol>
	 <p> Bangladesh <strong> is a </strong> developing <em> country</em>
	 
	</body>
</html>















